That's what I'm calling it anyway...

http://nevt.sourceforge.net/

I released this in a pretty slapdash manner...I hope to 
I've just bundled up the style sheets, DTDs, sample XML and SVG files
into a .zip file.  There's also a user guide, which I hope to flesh
out in better detail (the main thing it's missing right now is a good
explanation of what the graphics actually show, though a lot of that
can probably be intuited).  Anyway, I'll be updating the style sheets
(and hopefully adding new ones) and user guide periodically.

Of course, if anyone here uses it, I'd love to hear any feedback on
how to make it better.

Derek
